{"tid":1560982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實呢個係一個好好機會向優質旅客宣傳香港","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T12:23:33.000Z","uid":4174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da6c159ca7347ca62432c30e3fdbc9d5ff514ea1","tid":1560982,"uid":4174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"年年話訪港旅客數字破記錄 但絕大部份都係水貨客同低質蝗團  其他國家都係下跌<br />\n<br />\n其實好多日韓台東南亞歐美旅客都鐘意香港有特色<br />\n但應該好多人都怕左蝗又迫  同埋覺得酒店貴<br />\n依家應該要同佢地宣傳下酒店同機票平左好多<br />\n去迪士尼 山頂 大佛 呢d 都唔使排隊<br />\n呢d 機會可一不可再 遲d 班蝗返黎又烏煙瘴氣<br />\n最重要同佢地講香港好安全 只要去d冇popo 地方<br />\n示威者唔好搞旅客 仲會幫手 又可以推介下行山景點<br />\n等d 商家佬/政府知道旅遊業唔係淨係靠大陸<br />\n<br />\n係時候要良幣驅逐劣幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03595e79957e26826b43cb8acedcc58d09dae042","tid":1560982,"uid":4174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:05:23.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"fce8a58fea58d3a3be95e6423fdf943ca49fc7b8","tid":1560982,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"319d196d676231cb275950335f43677c206d31e4","tid":1560982,"uid":4174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":